# ── xStocks Calculator — environment variables ──────────────────────────────
# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in. All VITE_* vars are exposed to the
# browser bundle, so only put PUBLIC / read-only values here — never secrets.

# ── SERVER-SIDE (recommended) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by the /api/rpc serverless proxy. NOT prefixed VITE_, so it stays server-side
# and never ships in the browser bundle. Set this in Vercel → Settings → Environment
# Variables (Production + Preview + Development). This is the endpoint that actually
# makes wallet reads work + fast.
# Create a free key at https://helius.dev (or https://dashboard.helius.dev).
# Example: https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
SOLANA_RPC_URL=

# NB : l'analyste IA macro est en BYOK (Bring Your Own Key) — chaque utilisateur
# saisit SA propre clé Anthropic dans l'UI (stockée dans son navigateur, appel
# direct à Anthropic). Aucune clé Anthropic n'est gérée côté serveur ici.

# ── BROWSER (local dev only) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Plain `vite` dev does not run serverless functions, so /api/rpc won't exist locally.
# For local development, point this directly at your RPC URL. Exposed to the browser
# (VITE_*), so use a key you don't mind being public, or use `vercel dev` instead.
VITE_SOLANA_RPC=
